social_posts.post_text: Leave it to @patron to turn a power station into one of the best parties of the summer to launch their new tequila EL CIELO. 💛 #CieloLife #PatrónElCielo.

This Canada Day long weekend, impress your guests with this mouthwatering and easy recipe using @trestellecheese bocconcini made with 100% Canadian Dairy! This bocconcini has a delicious, fresh, mild and milky taste and is the perfect addition to these shareable Summer Antipasto Skewers.

 

Ingredients:

 

- Tre Stelle Mini Mini Bocconcini 

- Marinated Artichokes 

- Sundried Tomato

- Olives

- Prosciutto 

- Coppa di Parma

Assemble ingredients on wooden skewers, drizzle with olive oil and serve!

 

Enjoy! 

 

#CanadaDayTreStelle #TastesLikeMore #TreStelle #Bocconcini *Ad
